high_descs: Move to the round table across the room.
Pick up the keys on the table.
Turn around and head to the red couch with the box on it.
Put the keys in the box on the couch.
Pick up the box with keys on the couch.
Turn around, bring the box with keys around to the other side of the coffee table.
Put the box with keys on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with keys in it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward a step, turn left, go forward to the couch, turn left, go forward to the round table.
Take the keys to the left of the vase on the table.
Turn around, go forward to the couch, turn right, go forward, turn left to the box on the couch. Go forward to the couch.
Put the keys in the box.
Take the box from the couch.
Turn right, go forward a step, turn right, go forward past the coffee table, turn right, go forward, turn right to face the coffee table.
Put the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with keys in it on a coffee table.
